'''雅克·马丁·巴尔赞'''（{{lang-en|Jacques Martin Barzun}}，{{IPAc-en|ˈ|b|ɑr|z|ən}}，{{bd|1907年|11月30日|2012年|10月25日|catIdx=Barzun}}）是一位[[法裔美国人|法国裔]][[美国|美国]][[历史学家|历史学家]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VYaqL9CjKHA|title=Remembering Jacques Barzun: The Age of the Individual: 500 Years Ago Today|publisher=Center on Capitalism and Society|date=November 29, 2017|access-date=February 12, 2019|archive-date=2019-12-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191223040937/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VYaqL9CjKHA|dead-url=no}}</ref>，主攻[[思想史|思想史]]和[[文化史|文化史]]，获得过美国[[總統自由勳章|總統自由勳章]]和[[法國榮譽軍團勳章|法國榮譽軍團勳章]]<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2012/10/26/arts/jacques-barzun-historian-and-scholar-dies-at-104.html |title=Jacques Barzun Dies at 104; Cultural Critic Saw the Sun Setting on the West |work=[[New_York_Times|New York Times]] |author=Edward Rothstein |date=October 25, 2012 |access-date=October 25, 2012 |archive-date=2019-09-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190928045055/https://www.nytimes.com/2012/10/26/arts/jacques-barzun-historian-and-scholar-dies-at-104.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，最主要作品有93岁高龄时出版的《{{le|从黎明到衰落|From Dawn to Decadence|从黎明到衰落：西方文化生活五百年，1500年至今}}》（''From Dawn to Decadence: 500 Years of Western Cultural Life''）<ref>{{cite news |date=October 26, 2012 |title=Jacques Barzun: An Appreciation |first=Joseph |last=Epstein |newspaper=[[Wall_Street_Journal|Wall Street Journal]] |url=https://www.wsj.com/articles/SB10001424052970204598504578080902026564368?mod=googlenews_wsj |accessdate=2021-01-04 |archive-date=2017-08-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170813013219/https://www.wsj.com/articles/SB10001424052970204598504578080902026564368?mod=googlenews_wsj |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

